quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"““E inu anthu anga! Chifukwa ninji, ine ndikukuitanirani ku chipulumutso ndipo inu mukundiitanira ku Moto?”"
  40,42,"““Mukundiitanira kuti ndimkane Allah, ndi kuphatikiza ndi milungu yonama yomwe ine sindikuidziwa, pomwe ine ndikukuitanirani kwa Mwini mphamvu zoposa, Wokhululuka kwambiri?”"
  40,43,"““Palibe chikaiko, ndithu zomwe mukundiitanirazo (kuti ndizipembedze) zilibe (kuyankha) pempho lililonse pano pa dziko lapansi ngakhale tsiku lachimaliziro. Ndipo kobwerera kwathu nkwa Allah basi. Ndipo, wopyola malire (a Allah) iwowo ndiwo anthu a ku Moto.”"
  40,44,"““Choncho posachedwa, mudzakumbukira zimene ndikukuuzanizi. Ndipo ine ndikutula zinthu zanga kwa Allah, ndithu Allah akuona za anthu Ake.”"
  40,45,“Choncho Allah adam’teteza ku zoipa zomwe adam’tchera. Ndipo chilango choipa chidawazungulira anthu a Farawo (pamodzi ndi iye mwini)
  40,46,"“Zilango za kumoto zikusonyezedwa kwa iwo mmawa ndi madzulo. Ndipo tsiku lomwe Qiyâma idzafika (kudzanenedwa): “Alowetseni anthu a Farawo ku chilango cha ukali kwambiri (choposa chomwe adalandira mmanda mwawo).”"
  40,47,"“Ndipo (akumbutse) pamene azidzatsutsana m’Moto! Pamene ofooka (amene amatsatira) adzanena kwa omwe adali kudzikweza: “Ndithu ife tidali otsatira anu; kodi simungathe kutichotsera gawo lina la chilango cha Moto?”"
  40,48,"“Awo amene adadzikweza adzati: “Ndithu ife tonse tili mommuno. Ndithu Allah waweruza kale pakati pa akapolo (Ake). (Choncho palibe chilichonse chimene tingaphulepo).”"
  40,49,"“Ndipo a ku Moto adzayankhula kwa (angelo) olondera Jahannam: “Mpempheni Mbuye wanu, atipeputsire chilangochi tsiku limodzi.”"